name: I LOVE UGLY - Dark Navy Blazer -50%
description:
In the 1960s men dressed like men. They wore blazer jackets, used type writers, smoked cigars and drunk whiskey. That inspired us, so we decided to create a blazer jacket with that picture in our mind's eye. They are making it easy to feel like that man from the 60s, perhaps you would have worked in advertising in a tower in New York, or written books in a country side in England. Over the decades fashion has changed, but a blazer is timeless. Perfect for wearing in your vintage Mercedes sports car, if you have one.

I.L.U made this jacket in two colours, the classic tweed and a dapper navy.

+ Paisly detail lining
+ Wooden kissing buttons on sleeves
+ Inside pockets on both sides
+ Middle Back Split
+ Single-vented "tail" style
+ Coin Pocket
+ Tailored fit
+ Double button hole on collar
+ Contrast cord under collar (hidden detail)

Main fabric - 50% wool / 50% polyester
Lining - 100% cotton
Sleeve Lining - 100% polyester

name: I LOVE UGLY - Black Parka Jacket
description:
For us, a Parka is an important part of any mans wardrobe. It is a garment with a rich history and has been developed from being an Inuit's main source of warmth to being a fashion essential we know today.

In this parka rendition we have added more functionality and detail. Featuring side stash pockets, to put your hands in on brisk mornings, improved heavy drill cotton for extra weather durability, custom embossed snap domes and genuine thick leather toggles.

I.L.U have designed this jacket in two simple and powerful colour ways. The plain black, and the two-tone black and beige.

+ Heavy-duty quality 100% cotton drill
+ Side stash pockets
+ Leather toggles
+ Leather embossed triangle
+ Custom embossed snap domes

Main fabric - 100% cotton
Lining fabric - 100% polyester
